tips.text: Food is great. The shop has been around since 1933 and I have been here ever since I was born. The shop makes me reminisense all the past times when I was here. Fried prawn and fried fish a must try!
Try red Seafood Tom Yam with coconut milk! It's insane!!!
Every single component on every single dish was executed with thoughtful perfection. And what stunned me was the faultless timing of their courses, which clearly evinced a solid kitchen.
